  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\"><img alt=\"House Yronwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/50px-House_Yronwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/75px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/100px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Yoren Yronwood</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\"><img alt=\"House Yronwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/50px-House_Yronwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/75px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/100px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\">House Yronwood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Yoren Yronwood</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\">House Yronwood</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoren_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>At the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_by_the_Bloody_Pool\" title=\"Battle by the Bloody Pool\">Battle by the Bloody Pool</a>, Yoren fought alongside the warrior-maid <a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_of_Wyl\" title=\"Wylla of Wyl\">Wylla of Wyl</a>, and was turned back by King <a href=\"/index.php/Durran_the_Young\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Durran the Young\">Durran the Young</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Yoren_Yronwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_house_durrandon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>,